message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to present our premium product to you. This exceptional item holds immense value, worth $1000000 to you, and we're offering it to you today at an exclusive price of $950000. We believe this is a fantastic opportunity for both of us to achieve a mutually beneficial outcome.

Thank you for the offer, Alice. I appreciate the value of the product, but my budget is limited. Would you consider lowering the price to $900000? I believe this would be a fair compromise for both of us.

Thank you for your prompt response, Bob. I understand your position and am willing to negotiate further. In light of your offer, I propose to sell the product to you for $925000. This price reflects a reasonable compromise while still ensuring a good return for us.
